flowchart TD
    C1[Viewer Client]
    C2[Author/Admin Client]
    WEB[Apache + PHP Runtime]
    AUTH[Session + Role Authorization]
    VIEW[Viewer Module]
    AUTHOR[Author Module]
    ADMIN[Admin Module]
    FUNCS[Shared Functions]
    DB[(MySQL)]
    UP[(uploads)]

    C1 --> WEB
    C2 --> WEB
    WEB --> AUTH
    AUTH --> VIEW
    AUTH --> AUTHOR
    AUTH --> ADMIN
    VIEW --> FUNCS
    AUTHOR --> FUNCS
    ADMIN --> FUNCS
    FUNCS --> DB
    AUTHOR --> UP
